WEBVTT

00:01.420 --> 00:03.290
Previously on Damages...

00:03.300 --> 00:04.650
Someone tried to kill me.

00:04.660 --> 00:07.020
And, uh, where is this body?

00:07.030 --> 00:08.360
I've been trying to reach patty.

00:08.370 --> 00:10.050
Go to the beach house.

00:10.060 --> 00:12.930
Patty, where the hell are you?

00:14.070 --> 00:15.690
Ellen wants to use your beach house.

00:15.700 --> 00:16.610
Be my guest.

00:16.620 --> 00:19.310
I am trying to settle this case.

00:19.320 --> 00:20.880
Try harder.

00:21.390 --> 00:22.770
Katie, katie, it's me.

00:22.780 --> 00:24.470
Start by looking into arlington.

00:24.480 --> 00:25.640
Arlington, Virginia.

00:25.650 --> 00:27.910
Some girl was killed in a car crash.

00:27.920 --> 00:29.050
It was frobisher's car.

00:29.060 --> 00:33.430
The girl's family went from living
in a trailer park to being the biggest
land owner in Arlington.

00:33.440 --> 00:37.250
I'm sorry, gregory, for everything.

00:38.940 --> 00:40.540
It's done.

