23:18.290 --> 23:22.220
He forced us to keep investigating
frobisher's stock broker

23:22.260 --> 23:26.070
months after it was clear
that it would be a dead end.

23:26.080 --> 23:28.550
Did you ever figure out moore's agenda?

23:28.560 --> 23:29.330
No.

23:29.340 --> 23:31.830
But, the weekend before
frobisher dumped his stock,

23:31.840 --> 23:35.160
