the accounting fraud in his company.

23:35.170 --> 23:38.660
- The same weekend frobisher was in palm beach.
- Yeah. Exactly.

23:38.670 --> 23:41.430
And you know where george
moore was that same weekend?

23:41.440 --> 23:43.350
No. We had no reason to look into that.

23:43.360 --> 23:46.990
Well, he was in jacksonville, florida, less
than four hours away,

23:47.000 --> 23:49.320
at an sec commissioners' retreat.

23:49.330 --> 23:51.400
George moore chose
that location himself.

23:51.410 --> 23:54.920
He said he wanted to play
the 17th hole at sawgrass.

23:58.980 --> 24:00.430
Good morning.

24:01.080 --> 24:03.470
- Arthur frobisher.
- Yeah.

24:04.590 --> 24:06.100
I know who you are.

24:06.510 --> 24:07.520
Yeah.

24:07.940 --> 24:10.780
I probably shouldn't
be talking to you, huh?

24:11.830 --> 24:13.480
How's the coffee here?

24:15.580 --> 24:19.700
You know, when I was your age, i
used to run from moments like this,

24:20.130 --> 24:23.830
standing two feet from
somebody who hates your guts.

24:24.730 --> 24:27.030
Now I live for this shit.

24:28.340 --> 24:34.010
Was your trip to palm beach in june
2002 primarily business or pleasure?

24:34.020 --> 24:34.950
Business.

24:34.960 --> 24:38.270
I was there to deliver
a speech at a luncheon.

24:38.280 --> 24:40.750
That's where you met katie connor?

24:40.760 --> 24:42.740
No, we never met in florida.

24:42.750 --> 24:45.940
I was told later that she
was one of the caterers.

24:45.950 --> 24:49.780
And, afterwards, you approached
her about financing a restaurant?

24:50.070 --> 24:53.460
My attorney contacted
her on my behalf, yes.

24:53.470 --> 24:57.270
Why such interest in a novice chef?

24:57.280 --> 24:59.530
Objection. Vague.

25:00.430 --> 25:05.990
At the luncheon, an herb-encrusted
pork loin made quite an impression.

25:06.000 --> 25:10.080
I was told later that it
was ms. Connor's creation.

25:11.020 --> 25:17.600
Yet your financing of ms. Connor's restaurant halted
shortly after she agreed to testify in this case.

25:18.580 --> 25:20.010
Why was that?

25:20.580 --> 25:25.220
