series of personal struggles.

25:27.920 --> 25:29.450
Exhibit 41.

25:29.850 --> 25:32.970
Please mark as exhibit 41.

25:32.980 --> 25:35.650
Do you recognize this man?

25:36.860 --> 25:38.970
No, I don'T.

25:39.580 --> 25:44.900
Let the record reflect that exhibit
41 is a photograph of gregory malina.

25:46.820 --> 25:51.190
Were you aware that mr. Malina was in
palm beach the same weekend you were?

25:52.060 --> 25:54.300
No. I've never seen him before.

25:54.310 --> 25:57.850
So you didn't know he was
romantically linked to ms. Connor?

25:58.660 --> 26:00.000
No, I did not.

26:00.010 --> 26:03.380
Or that he owned a thousand
shares of stock in your company?

26:04.050 --> 26:07.420
My stock was publicly traded.
A lot of people had it.

26:07.430 --> 26:12.590
Or that in june,2002,he sold his stock
the very same morning you sold yours?

26:14.700 --> 26:16.950
No. No, I didn't know that.

26:20.410 --> 26:23.110
Are you aware mr. Malina is dead?

26:27.520 --> 26:29.040
No. No.

26:32.680 --> 26:36.000
But, like I said, I've
never seen this man before.

26:38.680 --> 26:41.130
I'm very sorry to hear that.

26:47.430 --> 26:50.260
I think that will be all for today.

27:01.690 --> 27:04.450
Did you give gregory
malina stock in my company?

27:04.460 --> 27:06.640
Absolutely not.

27:08.980 --> 27:10.790
Then who the hell tipped him off?

27:10.800 --> 27:12.690
I have no idea.

27:12.700 --> 27:15.390
It doesn't matter, art.
Malina can't hurt you.

27:16.740 --> 27:21.280
You know what i think? I think george
moore engineered this whole hit-and-run.

27:22.530 --> 27:26.050
Well, george is capable
of a lot of things.

27:27.800 --> 27:29.580
What does that mean? What do you mean?

27:30.780 --> 27:32.760
I think he leaked arlington.

27:32.770 --> 27:34.850
Well, for christ... Why would he do that?

27:34.860 --> 27:37.330
Save his own ass. Get you to settle.

27:38.870 --> 27:39.860
No, don'T...

27:39.870 --> 27:42.660
Senior partners wanted to meet with you.

27:43.420 --> 27:45.710
- We'll talk about this later.
