27:45.720 --> 27:47.830
Hey, marshall, come on in.

27:47.840 --> 27:49.410
Amos, good to see you.

27:49.420 --> 27:52.510
Arthur, you remember marshall
phillips, amos denninger,

27:52.520 --> 27:55.970
my superiors in everything
but shortness and baldness.

27:56.790 --> 27:58.080
Come on in. Sit down.

27:58.090 --> 27:59.620
Amos, you look good.

27:59.770 --> 28:00.900
Thank you very much.

28:00.910 --> 28:05.680
