one of our firm's resources is at your disposal.

28:05.690 --> 28:08.390
Well, marshall, i appreciate
that, but I'll tell you something.

28:08.400 --> 28:11.860
With ray, here, I never
felt more confident.

28:13.080 --> 28:14.610
Can I get you fellas a drink?

28:14.620 --> 28:16.460
