Will do.

31:52.570 --> 31:53.650
Ellen?

31:56.490 --> 31:58.240
I was just fired.

31:58.250 --> 31:59.610
What happened?

31:59.620 --> 32:02.180
The thing is, I'm fine.

32:02.690 --> 32:05.150
Seriously, I feel great.

32:05.160 --> 32:06.980
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

32:07.850 --> 32:09.700
Let's go out.

32:09.710 --> 32:11.220
Let's get drunk.

32:11.230 --> 32:13.620
We still have some friends, don't we?

32:15.700 --> 32:17.920
