32:36.300 --> 32:37.380
Where did you get this?

32:37.390 --> 32:39.820
The papers were filed this morning.

32:42.000 --> 32:43.330
God...

32:48.060 --> 32:49.910
who else knows about this?

32:49.920 --> 32:52.990
Well, it's just us and the
court... it's not public yet.

32:53.480 --> 32:56.170
Look, l-I'm going to
reschedule today's session.

32:56.180 --> 32:57.580
No. No, no, no.

32:57.590 --> 32:59.170
I've prepared for this.

32:59.180 --> 33:01.730
Art... art, listen to me.

33:01.740 --> 33:07.610
You are distracted. I cannot have you in
