40:37.430 --> 40:38.990
More than fair.

40:39.860 --> 40:41.550
Let's wrap this up.

40:46.090 --> 40:47.370
Patty?

40:48.690 --> 40:51.090
Oh, it's tempting, ray.

40:52.390 --> 40:54.510
I could use a vacation.

40:55.300 --> 40:57.010
