I don't even want a goddamn centerpiece.

42:43.200 --> 42:43.840
Oh, my god!

42:43.850 --> 42:45.270
Sorry, I didn't realize
it was the honeymoon.

42:45.280 --> 42:46.800
I'm sorry. I hate that shit.

42:51.930 --> 42:53.500
You were right.

42:55.070 --> 42:58.460
Whoever tried to clean up
the body missed something.

42:58.470 --> 42:59.640
What?

42:59.650 --> 43:02.030
Blood. I saw... the blood.

43:02.040 --> 43:04.200
Look, l-I got to take
this to the police.

43:04.210 --> 43:05.820
Did you get any word from patty?

43:05.830 --> 43:07.380
I've left messages.

43:07.390 --> 43:09.090
I've told her that she's
got to come back here.

43:09.100 --> 43:10.850
She doesn't want to come back.

43:10.860 --> 43:12.390
Why not?

43:18.230 --> 43:19.660
Ellen...

43:20.560 --> 43:24.930
patty is a lot of things, but
